Function LenByte(ByVal s)

    Dim c, i, k

    c = 0

    For i = 0 To Len(s) - 1
        k = Mid(s, i + 1, 1)

        If (Asc(k) And &HFF00) = 0 Then
            c = c + 1
        Else
            c = c + 2
        End If
    Next

    LenByte = c

End Function
